This paper discusses the use of visual odometry in mobile robots, which is a topic that falls under the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of cameras and image processing techniques, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of deep learning methods is also mentioned, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Finally, the paper discusses the challenges of localization and mapping, which are related to control systems (cs.SY).
